maxiofs (0.4.2-beta) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major feature release: S3 Compatibility, Real-Time Notifications & Dynamic Security
  * Global bucket uniqueness - bucket names unique across all tenants (AWS S3 compatible)
  * S3-compatible URLs - presigned URLs without tenant prefix
  * S3-compatible share URLs - standard S3 URL format
  * Automatic tenant resolution - backend resolves bucket ownership from name
  * Bucket Notifications (Webhooks) - AWS S3 compatible event notifications
  * Event types: ObjectCreated:*, ObjectRemoved:*, ObjectRestored:Post
  * Webhook delivery with retry mechanism (3 attempts, 2-second delay)
  * Per-rule filtering with prefix and suffix support
  * Custom HTTP headers support per notification rule
  * Web Console UI with tab-based bucket settings for notifications
  * Server-Sent Events (SSE) for real-time push notifications to admins
  * NotificationHub with automatic SSE client connection management
  * User locked notifications sent immediately when accounts are blocked
  * Topbar bell icon with unread count badge and notification dropdown
  * Read/unread state tracking with localStorage persistence
  * Limited to last 3 notifications to prevent UI clutter
  * Tenant isolation in notifications (global/tenant admin filtering)
  * Dynamic security configuration without server restart
  * Configurable IP-based rate limiting (security.ratelimit_login_per_minute)
  * Configurable account lockout threshold (security.max_failed_attempts)
  * Configurable lockout duration (security.lockout_duration)
  * Settings Manager integration with auth manager for dynamic rates
  * Fixed critical rate limiter double-counting bug (blocking at 3 instead of 5)
  * Fixed failed attempts counter not resetting after lockout
  * Fixed security page not showing locked users (camelCase field)
  * Fixed SSE callback not executing (type signature mismatch)
  * Fixed frontend token detection with periodic checking
  * Fixed streaming unsupported error (Flusher interface implementation)
  * Fixed presigned URL modal state persistence bug
  * Complete documentation updates (CHANGELOG, README, TODO, SECURITY)

 -- MaxIOFS Team <info@maxiofs.com>  Sun, 24 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000

